1
00:00:38,820 --> 00:00:40,820
=Visage and Soul=

2
00:00:40,820 --> 00:00:43,040
(The "Different Her"
Trilogy on Women's Relationships)

3
00:00:44,720 --> 00:00:47,640
=Episode 3=

4
00:00:53,840 --> 00:00:54,840
Xiaomi,

5
00:00:55,480 --> 00:00:56,720
listen to me.

6
00:00:57,480 --> 00:00:59,200
If you've forgotten, just let it be.

7
00:01:03,200 --> 00:01:03,960
Xiaomi,

8
00:01:04,400 --> 00:01:06,080
I just heard from Zhiwei
that you've lost your memory.

9
00:01:06,080 --> 00:01:07,200
Is that true?

10
00:01:08,160 --> 00:01:09,360
Who are you?

11
00:01:10,800 --> 00:01:11,640
Back in high school,

12
00:01:11,640 --> 00:01:13,840
I bought breakfast for you every day.

13
00:01:16,560 --> 00:01:18,080
You really don't remember me?

14
00:01:18,720 --> 00:01:20,520
I'm Xu Yifei.

15
00:01:22,080 --> 00:01:23,360
Xu Yifei?

16
00:01:23,920 --> 00:01:25,240
That's right, Xiaomi.

17
00:01:25,600 --> 00:01:27,560
I honestly never thought
I'd see you again.

18
00:01:31,240 --> 00:01:32,840
If it weren't for Ye Xiaoduo,

19
00:01:33,000 --> 00:01:34,400
you wouldn't have ended up

20
00:01:34,400 --> 00:01:36,240
like this after that fire.

21
00:01:37,000 --> 00:01:38,880
That scheming little witch

22
00:01:39,120 --> 00:01:41,520
got exactly what she deserved.

23
00:01:42,600 --> 00:01:45,000
I remember back in high school,
she was already manipulative.

24
00:01:45,000 --> 00:01:46,280
Just thinking about her makes me mad.

25
00:01:47,040 --> 00:01:48,160
Give me back my bag!

26
00:01:48,400 --> 00:01:48,800
Or I'll...

27
00:01:48,800 --> 00:01:49,680
Your bag?

28
00:01:49,680 --> 00:01:50,520
You thief!

29
00:01:50,520 --> 00:01:52,000
Give Xiaomi's phone back, right now!

30
00:01:52,000 --> 00:01:52,840
Ye Xiaoduo,

31
00:01:52,840 --> 00:01:54,120
are you asking for trouble?

32
00:01:56,480 --> 00:01:58,160
Give it back!

33
00:02:33,200 --> 00:02:34,480
Teacher!

34
00:02:35,440 --> 00:02:36,360
Ye Xiaoduo!

35
00:02:37,880 --> 00:02:38,800
Ye Xiaoduo!

36
00:02:39,360 --> 00:02:40,960
You don't even remember her?

37
00:02:41,200 --> 00:02:43,720
Ye Xiaoduo was your father's
illegitimate daughter.

38
00:02:44,000 --> 00:02:45,600
Everyone knew she was jealous of you

39
00:02:45,600 --> 00:02:46,920
and wanted to take everything you had.

40
00:02:47,920 --> 00:02:48,960
I also heard

41
00:02:48,960 --> 00:02:51,120
that she started the fire.

42
00:02:53,200 --> 00:02:54,160
Xiaomi,

43
00:02:54,160 --> 00:02:55,280
are you okay?

44
00:02:56,520 --> 00:02:57,360
Xiaomi?

45
00:03:03,560 --> 00:03:05,880
Didn't Dad say the fire was an accident?

46
00:03:06,400 --> 00:03:08,600
Why did he never mention Ye Xiaoduo?

47
00:03:16,600 --> 00:03:17,480
You're distracted.

48
00:03:17,680 --> 00:03:18,640
It's not safe to drive like this.

49
00:03:18,640 --> 00:03:19,360
I'll take you.

50
00:03:20,120 --> 00:03:21,480
Don't ask me why I'm here.

51
00:03:21,840 --> 00:03:23,360
And don't ask what I'm trying to do.

52
00:03:24,800 --> 00:03:26,240
I'm your fiancé.

53
00:03:26,240 --> 00:03:27,960
Of course I'm going
to keep an eye on you,

54
00:03:27,960 --> 00:03:28,880
and protect you.

55
00:03:37,160 --> 00:03:38,640
Do you know Ye Xiaoduo?

56
00:03:39,800 --> 00:03:40,640
Of course.

57
00:03:40,960 --> 00:03:42,600
She's your half-sister.

58
00:03:44,760 --> 00:03:46,040
Did something come back to you?

59
00:03:56,680 --> 00:03:58,120
You don't look well at all.

60
00:03:58,400 --> 00:03:59,440
You need to relax.

61
00:04:13,160 --> 00:04:14,320
How did I fall asleep?

62
00:04:14,840 --> 00:04:15,680
You're asking me?

63
00:04:18,600 --> 00:04:19,760
Where am I?

64
00:04:21,720 --> 00:04:22,640
An herbal clinic.

65
00:04:24,240 --> 00:04:25,840
Why am I at an herbal clinic?

66
00:04:26,640 --> 00:04:28,080
I brought you here to help you relax.

67
00:04:32,040 --> 00:04:33,040
As for why you fell asleep

68
00:04:33,040 --> 00:04:34,640
the moment you walked in,
I have no idea.

69
00:04:35,160 --> 00:04:36,440
It's been two hours already.

70
00:04:38,520 --> 00:04:40,200
The scent here

71
00:04:40,200 --> 00:04:41,360
feels so familiar to me.

72
00:04:42,320 --> 00:04:43,320
It makes me feel safe.

73
00:04:50,680 --> 00:04:51,880
The smell of mugwort.

74
00:05:10,200 --> 00:05:11,080
Don't be afraid.

75
00:05:11,720 --> 00:05:12,760
Take my hand.

76
00:05:13,400 --> 00:05:14,920
I'll take you somewhere safe.

77
00:05:17,880 --> 00:05:19,000
Who are you?

78
00:05:21,960 --> 00:05:23,400
Who exactly are you?

79
00:05:28,120 --> 00:05:29,800
Why did you bring me here?
What are you really after?

80
00:05:31,080 --> 00:05:32,360
To help you relax.

81
00:05:33,680 --> 00:05:35,320
And see if it helps you
remember anything.

82
00:05:35,760 --> 00:05:37,160
What do you want me to remember?

83
00:05:39,560 --> 00:05:40,440
Me.

84
00:05:57,560 --> 00:05:58,720
What are you looking for?

85
00:05:59,000 --> 00:06:00,040
Let me help.

86
00:06:01,360 --> 00:06:02,560
If you dare gamble again,

87
00:06:02,560 --> 00:06:03,960
I swear I'll kick you out.

88
00:06:04,360 --> 00:06:05,200
What are you talking about,

89
00:06:05,200 --> 00:06:06,400
my dear sister?

90
00:06:08,640 --> 00:06:10,560
Father left you so much money.

91
00:06:10,560 --> 00:06:11,680
Can you even spend it all?

92
00:06:28,240 --> 00:06:30,760
Was Ye Xiaoduo really
Dad's illegitimate daughter?

93
00:06:31,040 --> 00:06:32,760
If everything they said is true,

94
00:06:33,240 --> 00:06:34,400
then why isn't there
a single trace of her

95
00:06:34,400 --> 00:06:35,800
anywhere in this house?

96
00:06:36,200 --> 00:06:37,040
Don't be afraid.

97
00:06:38,280 --> 00:06:39,720
I'll take you somewhere safe.

98
00:06:40,520 --> 00:06:41,640
Could it be

99
00:06:41,640 --> 00:06:44,040
she's the girl from my dreams?

100
00:06:44,440 --> 00:06:45,680
But why

101
00:06:46,080 --> 00:06:47,400
didn't I feel

102
00:06:47,400 --> 00:06:49,240
even the slightest bit
of hostility from her?

103
00:07:07,880 --> 00:07:08,760
Xiaomi.

104
00:07:10,360 --> 00:07:11,320
Xiaomi.

105
00:07:32,960 --> 00:07:33,960
Xiaomi!

106
00:07:37,200 --> 00:07:38,480
What a lunatic!

107
00:07:44,600 --> 00:07:45,600
Morning, Xiaomi.

108
00:07:46,480 --> 00:07:47,160
Look.

109
00:07:47,440 --> 00:07:48,960
I picked these shoes just for you.

110
00:07:49,200 --> 00:07:50,400
Perfect for a morning workout.

111
00:07:51,960 --> 00:07:53,560
Do you even know what time it is?

112
00:07:54,320 --> 00:07:55,800
Did you forget our agreement?

113
00:07:56,200 --> 00:07:57,640
If you want to start painting again,

114
00:07:58,000 --> 00:07:59,600
you need a healthy body first.

115
00:08:04,120 --> 00:08:05,200
As long as you stop bothering me,

116
00:08:05,720 --> 00:08:06,600
I'm perfectly healthy.

117
00:08:07,200 --> 00:08:07,920
Fine.

118
00:08:08,560 --> 00:08:10,080
But if you stay this weak,

119
00:08:10,560 --> 00:08:11,800
everything in the Qiao family

120
00:08:12,000 --> 00:08:13,360
will end up in Qiao Zhiwei's hands.

121
00:08:13,760 --> 00:08:16,360
You could've waited until I woke up.

122
00:08:26,160 --> 00:08:27,120
I'm going to change.

123
00:08:38,480 --> 00:08:40,280
Let's start with a two-kilometer jog.

124
00:08:40,560 --> 00:08:42,120
I'll teach you how to pace yourself
and breathe properly.

125
00:08:43,040 --> 00:08:45,200
Do you know that waking up early
ruins the whole day?

126
00:08:45,560 --> 00:08:46,800
You agreed to let me help you

127
00:08:46,800 --> 00:08:48,320
recover your memories within two months.

128
00:08:48,320 --> 00:08:49,360
For these two months,

129
00:08:50,360 --> 00:08:51,960
you do as I say.

130
00:08:55,160 --> 00:08:56,360
Unless

131
00:08:56,360 --> 00:08:57,480
you can beat me.

132
00:08:59,360 --> 00:09:00,760
See that streetlight over there?

133
00:09:01,040 --> 00:09:02,000
Whoever gets there

134
00:09:02,160 --> 00:09:02,800
first...

135
00:09:07,120 --> 00:09:08,360
Relax your shoulders.

136
00:09:08,760 --> 00:09:10,160
Lean your weight forward.

137
00:09:11,000 --> 00:09:12,160
Swing your arms.

138
00:09:12,160 --> 00:09:13,360
Let them drive your movement.

139
00:09:14,440 --> 00:09:16,000
In through your nose,
out through your mouth.

140
00:09:16,760 --> 00:09:17,440
That's it.

141
00:09:17,760 --> 00:09:18,880
Just like that.

142
00:09:20,000 --> 00:09:21,480
That voice...

143
00:09:21,800 --> 00:09:23,120
What is it?

144
00:09:35,520 --> 00:09:36,840
How can you run so fast?

145
00:09:38,720 --> 00:09:39,600
Convinced now?

146
00:09:39,880 --> 00:09:40,960
From now on, if you want to run,
do it yourself.

147
00:09:45,360 --> 00:09:47,400
You got a head start, okay?

148
00:09:47,920 --> 00:09:48,760
One more round.

149
00:09:59,200 --> 00:10:00,120
Dr. Chen.

150
00:10:01,920 --> 00:10:02,840
Qiao Xiaomi?

151
00:10:03,640 --> 00:10:04,800
Why is it you?

152
00:10:06,680 --> 00:10:07,680
I...

153
00:10:08,080 --> 00:10:10,000
I've lost some of my memories.

154
00:10:10,360 --> 00:10:11,640
I'd like to ask for your help.

155
00:10:15,080 --> 00:10:16,600
Have you seen a psychologist before?

156
00:10:20,000 --> 00:10:22,400
The doctor said
my chances of recovery were near zero.

157
00:10:23,760 --> 00:10:25,640
From a psychological perspective,

158
00:10:26,000 --> 00:10:27,400
memories can be rebuilt.

159
00:10:28,000 --> 00:10:29,520
But you need a trigger.

160
00:10:30,680 --> 00:10:32,040
It could be a place,

161
00:10:32,560 --> 00:10:33,720
an object,

162
00:10:35,440 --> 00:10:36,680
or perhaps...

163
00:10:39,440 --> 00:10:40,440
a person.

164
00:10:42,000 --> 00:10:42,920
A person?

165
00:10:44,120 --> 00:10:45,440
Could that person

166
00:10:45,440 --> 00:10:47,200
be Qin Yu?

167
00:11:17,520 --> 00:11:19,590
♪We say good morning,
we say good night♪

168
00:11:19,590 --> 00:11:23,010
♪We say we miss each other,
but never speak of the hurt♪

169
00:11:24,610 --> 00:11:26,500
♪The sweeter it is,
the luckier we seem♪

170
00:11:26,500 --> 00:11:30,490
♪Yet the more romantic,
the rougher the road♪

171
00:11:31,730 --> 00:11:33,590
♪Let me go, set me free♪

172
00:11:33,590 --> 00:11:37,630
♪Let me drown in reckless silence♪

173
00:11:38,170 --> 00:11:43,580
♪We were perfect for each other,
yet you never admitted it♪

174
00:11:44,930 --> 00:11:47,070
♪The freedom you gave me♪

175
00:11:47,070 --> 00:11:50,710
♪Became the heaviest chain I bear♪

176
00:11:51,970 --> 00:11:54,240
♪Love can barely move forward♪

177
00:11:54,240 --> 00:11:58,020
♪Yet the words still linger unspoken♪

178
00:11:59,120 --> 00:12:01,360
♪The closeness I long for♪

179
00:12:01,360 --> 00:12:05,750
♪There's no need for you
to keep avoiding it♪

180
00:12:06,160 --> 00:12:07,980
♪I don't want to break free♪

181
00:12:07,980 --> 00:12:13,350
♪Take back the chains
disguised as freedom♪

